<script>
	import CodeShowBlock from '$components/CodeShowBlock.svelte';
	import svlatepickr from '$lib';
</script>

<h1>Welcome to Svelte Flatpickr Plus</h1>

<p>
	Flatpickr is a lightweight and powerful datetime picker. Svelte Flatpickr Plus is a wrapper for
	Flatpickr with some extra features.
</p>
<hr />
<h2>What is difference from Svelte Flatpickr ?</h2>
<ul>
	<li>
		Svelte Flatpickr Plus is just a svelte actions that you can using with use:action directive of
		svelte on input element with any class or style
	</li>
	<li>
		You can using your locale years (e.g. Buddhist Era) with <code>useLocaleYear</code> option.
	</li>
	<li>
		You can setting a reset behavior with <code>resetMoveDefault</code> and
		<code>resetToDefault</code> option.
	</li>
	<li>
		On a calendar, year input has been replace with year dropdown element for easy to select year.
	</li>
	<li>
		Have theme changer plugin to calling and change a theme of calendar while theme has been
		changed.
	</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h2 id="basic_usage">Basic Usage<a href="#basic_usage" class="permalink">ðŸ”—</a></h2>
<div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
	<h3>First let import actions</h3>
	<p style="margin-top:0;">
		you can name the actions as you like
		<br />
		but in this document I will calling it &nbsp;
		<b style="font-size:1.25rem"><i>svlatepickr</i></b> &nbsp;(svelte + flatpickr)
	</p>
	<CodeShowBlock
		hideTitle={true}
		code={`<script>
  //you can name the actions as you like..
  import svlatepickr from 'svelte-flatpickr-plus';
</script>`}
		style="max-width:25rem;"
	/>
</div>
<hr />
<div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem;">
	<div class="element-block">
		<h3>Date Picker</h3>
		<div>
			<input use:svlatepickr placeholder="please select date" readonly />
		</div>
	</div>
	<CodeShowBlock code={`<input use:svlatepickr placeholder="please select date" readonly />`} />
</div>
<hr />
<div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem;">
	<div class="element-block">
		<h3>Multiple Date Picker</h3>
		<div>
			<input
				use:svlatepickr={{ mode: 'multiple' }}
				placeholder="please select multiple date"
				readonly
			/>
		</div>
	</div>
	<CodeShowBlock
		code={`<input use:svlatepickr={{ mode: 'multiple' }} placeholder="please select multiple date" readonly />`}
	/>
</div>
<hr />
<div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem;">
	<div class="element-block">
		<h3>Date Range Picker</h3>
		<div>
			<input use:svlatepickr={{ mode: 'range' }} placeholder="please select date range" readonly />
		</div>
	</div>

	<CodeShowBlock
		code={`<input use:svlatepickr={{ mode: 'range' }} placeholder="please select date range" readonly />`}
	/>
</div>
<hr />
<div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem;">
	<div class="element-block">
		<h3>Month Picker</h3>
		<div>
			<input use:svlatepickr={{ isMonthPicker: true }} placeholder="please select month" readonly />
		</div>
	</div>

	<CodeShowBlock
		code={`<input use:svlatepickr={{ isMonthPicker: true }} placeholder="please select month" readonly />`}
	/>
</div>
<hr />
<div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem;">
	<div class="element-block">
		<h3>Multiple Month Picker</h3>
		<div>
			<input
				use:svlatepickr={{ mode: 'multiple', isMonthPicker: true }}
				placeholder="please select multiple month"
				readonly
			/>
		</div>
	</div>

	<CodeShowBlock
		code={`<input use:svlatepickr={{ mode: 'multiple', isMonthPicker: true }} placeholder="please select multiple month" readonly />`}
	/>
</div>
<hr />
<div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem;">
	<div class="element-block">
		<h3>Month Range Picker</h3>
